  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  color: inherit;
  border-left: .25em solid #888;

  margin-top: 0

  margin-bottom: 0

  font-weight: 500;
  align-items: center;

  fill: currentColor;

  border-left-color: var(--color-note);

  color: var(--color-note);
